WWW::Trello::Lite

Copyright 2013  Robert Wohlfarth <rbwohlfarth@gmail.com>

You can redistribute and/or modify this module under the same terms as Perl
itself.


Trello (https://www.trello.com) manages lists of stuff. Trello provides an API
for remote control. WWW::Trello::Lite gives Perl scripts easy access to the
API. I use it to add cards on my to-do list.
